dcterms:description: The OCT2017 dataset contains 84,484 images provided as high quality TIFF format with 3 non-RGB color channels, aimed at recognizing and differentiating between four distinct retinal states: normal healthy retina, Drusen, Choroidal Neovascularization (CNV), and Diabetic Macular Edema (DME).
dcterms:title: OCT2017

dcterms:description: The Srinivasan2014 dataset consists of 3,231 image samples aimed at classifying normal healthy specimens of retina, Age-Related Macular Degeneration (AMD), and Diabetic Macular Edema (DME).
dcterms:title: Srinivasan2014
